00:25:02,760 --> 00:25:05,880
"He forced me to continue training.
So I fled,

368
00:25:06,280 --> 00:25:08,960
"like a criminal. See?

369
00:25:09,160 --> 00:25:11,880
"I took refuge in the forest.
