Tell him I'll be there soon.

423
00:31:52,840 --> 00:31:54,720
I'm sorry.
I won't be long.

424
00:32:03,080 --> 00:32:05,200
She leaves him, unceremoniously.

425
00:32:05,400 --> 00:32:08,040
So he hits a rough patch

426
