I mean, untangling lots of threads.

460
00:33:44,840 --> 00:33:47,080
I'm breaking out of a deadlock.

461
00:33:47,280 --> 00:33:49,520
That's great, that's great...

462
00:33:51,840 --> 00:33:53,280
I'm sorry, Antoine,

463
